{"tid":1611254,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"葉劉淑儀: 對於英國外交官Dominic Raab散播未經證實的消息感到十分失望","createTime":"2019-10-02T02:05:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T10:39:07.000Z","uid":167469,"like":9,"dislike":67,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"b2cfbb6d1497addf11dd2716e55a33796a0aec61","tid":1611254,"uid":167469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:05:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">I was dismayed to note that Britain&rsquo;s Foreign Secretary Dominic Raab, MP, commenting on the violence which rocked Hong Kong yesterday, 1 October, called the Police&rsquo;s use of live ammunition &ldquo;inappropriate&rdquo;.</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nSuch comments made thousands of miles away by a foreign official, in the absence of any first-hand knowledge of what actually happened on the ground, are inappropriate and unjustified.<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong&rsquo;s well trained Police Force use live ammunition in accordance with strict instructions - only when their lives and those of others are in jeopardy. As our Commissioner of Police Stephen Lo has explained, yesterday a Policeman was under attack by rioters using sharp poles, bricks and stones and another Policeman had to fire a shot to stop the violence.<br />\n<br />\nNo doubt Hong Kong&rsquo;s Police Force would conduct its own internal investigation to establish how the event occurred. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">But it is totally inappropriate for foreign officials to pass unwarranted judgments not supported by facts. Such biased comments indirectly fuel the escalating cycle of violence in Hong Kong.</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nI also note with great concern that the injured person is a secondary school student of young age. I call upon all parents, all teachers, indeed all mature individuals to remind our young people not to persist in breaking the law and destroying our social order in the name of democracy and freedom.<br />\n<br />\nPursuit of democracy or freedom by violent means give these causes a bad name. Hong Kong as a whole has suffered a lot since 9 June. It is high time such mindless and unjustified violence stop.<br />\n<br />\nsource: 葉劉淑儀facrebook"},{"pid":"395b2305d9d0b6064cabedfd99b50e0331c28c06","tid":1611254,"uid":34334,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:06:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f364299dcc4599d771ea5e293685cb28b6dd446","tid":1611254,"uid":32588,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:07:28.000Z","msg":"英國都要加入一齊制裁賣港官員議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0b95242471f42f876607d8b0b023317d9f920da","tid":1611254,"uid":166857,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:07:32.000Z","msg":"睇得出有人驚到瀨尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e4a53079c56c81728510b7985ccc61985b22084","tid":1611254,"uid":160842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:08:14.000Z","msg":"今日12點半，黑西裝癱瘓全中環！！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610862\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1610862</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fZNuSLH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfZNuSLH.jpg&h=d4aeaf4f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RFKhhcn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRFKhhcn.jpg&h=47eada71&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iQ5gxLJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiQ5gxLJ.jpg&h=332903b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"23f6d33a8d8657ff176d3dded956f2d37241d74b","tid":1611254,"uid":272652,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:08:26.000Z","msg":"將啲美金換定人民幣啦孽瘤"},{"pid":"672d0084123bca706e801fa9563a9d01a67cfb19","tid":1611254,"uid":21545,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:09:55.00